name: Architectural_Wall_Cabinet,_White_with_Indigo_interior
reviews: Was surprised at how much I love this cabinet. It will hang in our loft as a curio cabinet for my small collection of antique creamers. Thanks Overstock for offering this.
Loved the wall cabinet. Been Loki g for just the right piece, and this is definitely it!

This is a very low quality piece. The finish is really rough and cheap-looking (maybe could work in a shabby chic environment). The glass was shipped right inside the cabinet, covered with a single piece of paper. It would have been a miracle if it had actually arrived in one piece but of course, it was shattered. Overstock sent a return label, and it was a quick process for a refund.
